sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ContentScript as Content Script
    participant Background as Background SW
    participant Offscreen as Offscreen Document
    participant IDB as IndexedDB

    User->>ContentScript: Types (debounced)
    ContentScript->>Background: { action: "searchMemory", query, limit }
    Background->>Offscreen: { action: "search", query, limit }
    Offscreen->>Offscreen: Embed query -> vector
    Offscreen->>IDB: getAll records
    IDB-->>Offscreen: all { text, embedding }
    Offscreen->>Offscreen: Compute cosine similarity, filter >0.7
    Offscreen-->>Background: { results: [...] }
    Background-->>ContentScript: results
    ContentScript->>ContentScript: Show MemoryChip with snippets
    User->>ContentScript: Clicks "Insert" on a snippet
    ContentScript->>ContentScript: Prepend context to input field